  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Businesses supplying medicines and medical devices – what to expect on day one of a ‘no deal’ scenario
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    If the UK leaves the EU without a deal, people should be reassured and have confidence in the government’s plans for continuity of medicines supply.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

