        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-contents-list__list-item gem-c-contents-list__list-item--dashed ">
          <a class="gem-c-contents-list__link " data-track-category="contentsClicked" data-track-action="content_item 5" data-track-label="#actions-you-can-take-now" data-track-options="{"dimension29":"Actions you can take now"}" href="#actions-you-can-take-now">Actions you can take now</a>
        </li>
